reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact and classy (for a broom)
reviews.reviewText: I love the compact size of this little whisk broom, and how the brush cleverly connects by magnet to it's dust pan, keeping the 2 pieces together! The bristles are not too soft nor too stiff to sweep debris off of our cars' mats. Due to its size, it stores very easily and attractively in the car. It's rather classy for a cleaning tool; rather than the typical plastic, I appreciate -- for both sturdiness and aesthetics -- the materials used for the brush and the dust pan!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very cute and doesn’t look like a brush!
reviews.reviewText: I needed a small brush and dustpan for my RV and found this to be the cutest one! Now, it is double the price of comparable others, however the shape of this brush is what made me pick it. From the backside it doesn’t look like a brush and this was the look I was going for!The brush is being held inside the dustbin by a magnet, which is a great idea.I am giving this brush 4 stars because I think it’s a cute little brush but the price point is very high. It ought to cost half of what it does!
